Many high-energy astrophysical environments are strongly magnetized, that is, the magnetic energy per particle exceeds the rest mass energy, so that the magnetization parameter σ ≡ B02∕4πnmec2≥1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
